ncy < 8.5 Hz) for a maximum depth of 8 km. Compared to the\nstarting model, FWI dramatically improves the reconstruction of the bounding\nfaults of the Gorgon horst at reservoir depths as well as several intra-horst\nfaults and several horizons of the Mungaroo formation down to a depth of 7 km.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 30 Oct 2022 08:06:28 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 11 Jan 2023 22:47:27 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-01-13"}
